FT  23 NOV 92 / World News in Brief: Iraq pessimistic on sanctions
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Iraq said it was not pinning much hope on a mission by deputy prime minister
Tariq Aziz to ask the UN Security Council to ease or lift sanctions in force
